HEADWORD: Threadfin
<hw>Thread"fin`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of fishes belonging to
<gen>Polynemus</gen> and allied genera. They have numerous long pectoral
filaments.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Threadfish</ent>⟦br⟧
